Language name: XIAMEN
Language number: 2504
Alternate names: Amoy
Classification: Sino-Tibetan, Sinitic
Comments: Xiamen is spoken in the southern Fujian, 
Guang-Dong, south Hainan Island, southern Zheijiang in 
China.

